title: Hazali Nasiron
text: Hazali Nasiron is a <a href="Singapore">Singapore</a>an <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Defender%20%28association%20football%29">Defender</a> who played for <a href="Singapore%20national%20football%20team">Singapore</a> in the <a href="1984%20Asian%20Cup">1984 Asian Cup</a>.
